	   <tr><td colspan=2>I've kind of decided to use a piercer in my secondary just because some guy randomly gave me a harpoon of the depths and a walrus tooth...which is better than a bronze short sword which is like 4 27 with no stats..AND, I don't have the money to spend on weapons, i have 55pp and still need to buy banded armor at lvl 11. So weapons are a little pricey but the harpoon and walrus tooth should easily keep me cool until lvl 18 or so when by then I should be able to buy a sturdy grimmling pick which will last for a long time. Plus, the centi line is expensive(too me at least) and there are a lot of good decent damage piercers out there i could pick up as well.<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;  Of course i could sell the tooth and buy a blackened alloy long sword, but then I'd have no money for armor... anyways i think a harpoon of the depths in my primary, walrus in my secondary, dragoon dirk in the range should work out pretty nice for atleast a while.<br><br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Thu Aug  1 17:31:21 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
